<section xml:id="sec_counting-binomial-coefficients" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Selections and Binomial Coefficients</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>In this section we introduce binomial coefficients and their 
    connection to making selections from a set of possible options. We 
    introduce the notation <m>\binom{n}{k}</m>, "<m>n</m> choose 
    <m>k</m>", to denote <m>\frac{n!}{\left(n - k\right)!\cdot k!}</m>.
    </p>
  </introduction>

</section>

